</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Mater à plus de 4 endroits avec un petit burin froid. 
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A311020.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.911mm" ver = "01" gw = "186" gh = "133"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "1.968in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1. 
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Matage 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Avec les outils spéciaux et une presse hydraulique, emmancher le moyeu de roue (1) dans le roulement de roue (2). 
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A114">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-75810">
 09913-75810 
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3A115">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09951-18211">
 09951-18211 
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A311017.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "57.910mm" ver = "01" gw = "203" gh = "148"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Brancher l&#39;arbre de roue sur le porte-fusée de direction. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A3116003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Brancher le porte-fusée de direction sur le bras de suspension. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A2206008"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Reposer les boulons de patte de jambe et les écrous. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A2206003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Poser le capteur de vitesse de roue avant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A4606007"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Brancher l&#39;embout de barre d&#39;accouplement sur le porte-fusée de direction. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A6306003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Poser le disque de frein arrière et l&#39;étrier de frein. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A4206005"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Serrer l&#39;écrou d&#39;arbre de roue au couple prescrit, puis mater l&#39;écrou d&#39;arbre de roue. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A3116003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Veiller à utiliser un écrou d&#39;arbre de roue neuf. 
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Reposer la roue avant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A2406001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Vérifier la géométrie des roues avant. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A2206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
</servinfotype>
</configtype>
</servcat>
